---
description: Rules for working with BitrixFramework
alwaysApply: true
---

- The project is engaged in the sale of cosmetics.
- The project uses the Bitrix Framework editorial online store version >= 26.150.0. All solutions must be compatible with the Bitrix architecture and standards.
- Consideration must be given to working with standard Bitrix classes, hooks, and event handlers.
- Code should be written using Bitrix Framework functions and classes whenever possible.
- Include classes by use instruction.
- You should place all helper methods and functions in local/php_interface/classes/Utils.php
- You must use @docs/1C-Bitrix api, @docs/1C-Bitrix Разработчик курс, @docs/1C-Bitrix Vue курс, @docs/IMask
- For tasks of bonuses system check module by directory @/bitrix/modules/aspro.bonus
- In templates of components do not include files like ./script.js and ./style.css, because they include automatically